snippet.title: Sirocco Gameplay Trailer Featuring Captains
snippet.description: MOBA meets Vampire Survivors in a dynamic 5v5 arena inspired by the legendary Warcraft 3 mod: Battleships. Rally your team as you swap abilities mid-match, load up auto-firing weapons, and craft strategies on the fly in Sirocco. No rules — just fun.
